{"tw": {"3264850": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "關於我轉生成為變態手的那檔事", "steam_appid": 3264850, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>💟OUR NEW GAME💟</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/1eecf9b93b0b6c75f65d3ba89c71762f.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/1eecf9b93b0b6c75f65d3ba89c71762f.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/1eecf9b93b0b6c75f65d3ba89c71762f.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7e3bf3e155e06a9e26f6cfa3508b3db0.avif?t=1775122300\" width=600 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《關於我轉生成為變態手的那檔事》</strong>是一款緊張刺激的roguelite遊戲，將快節奏的動作玩法與搞笑幽默、出人意料的樂趣融為一體！每一局都是全新的體驗。去吧，面對意想不到的挑戰，打造屬於你自己的獨特之手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/79a1ffbee79f9dc7ef74cf91db53a637.avif?t=1775122300\" width=289 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >易於上手，只需 <strong>騷擾和拍打</strong> 即可獲勝！遊戲的核心機制非常簡單，卻能帶來<strong>極大的滿足感。</strong>你將控制一隻變態手，使用一系列基於拍打的攻擊和技巧。騷擾敵人，玩弄對手，在最佳時刻發動完美攻擊，取得勝利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可愛又性感的怪物遍佈各個角落，為你的冒險之旅增添一絲幽默。你的對手也許是無禮的魅魔、頑皮的史萊姆，或是其他各種天馬行空的敵人，每個怪物都經過了獨特的設計，既具有挑戰性，又能讓人享受其中。當你制定下一步行動策略時，這些挑逗又有趣的角色會讓你保持警覺！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲有 <strong>7個主屬性系統</strong>，讓你可以從多方面打造手的能力。從力量到運氣，在對付不同的小怪和頭目時，每個屬性都會扮演至關重要的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/4a9697322b270bb9272374472583397b.avif?t=1775122300\" width=320 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多種技能，不同用法。</strong> 手的潛能無窮無盡。升級從「華麗攻擊」到「巧妙躲避」等各種技能，並進行適合你策略的混搭使用。無論你是喜歡殘酷直擊還是戰術控制，靈活的技能組合都能確保每局遊戲精彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3a598102d3fa61fb0f52e9e211a5552a.avif?t=1775122300\" width=283 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品豐富，玩法多樣。</strong> 遊戲中有無數種方法能增加手的能力。收集強大的神器，解鎖全新的協同作用，改變你的戰鬥策略。這些物品不僅是為了展示，更能徹底改變你的戰鬥方式，並幫助你在最艱難的挑戰中佔優勢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/00d9c94ab877bd13bd560d2b26ba19e5.avif?t=1775122300\" width=597 height=88 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>還有一點也很重要：在擊敗Boss後，可以與她們分享極緻美好時刻。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3a40dc23c971de69c77961cfa185f9d4.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3a40dc23c971de69c77961cfa185f9d4.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3a40dc23c971de69c77961cfa185f9d4.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7e3bf3e155e06a9e26f6cfa3508b3db0.avif?t=1775122300\" width=600 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《關於我轉生成為變態手的那檔事》</strong>是一款緊張刺激的roguelite遊戲，將快節奏的動作玩法