></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物品豐富，玩法多樣。</strong> 遊戲中有無數種方法能增加手的能力。收集強大的神器，解鎖全新的協同作用，改變你的戰鬥策略。這些物品不僅是為了展示，更能徹底改變你的戰鬥方式，並幫助你在最艱難的挑戰中佔優勢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3169fe9f2988bdd43576d69ebbdce481.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/00d9c94ab877bd13bd560d2b26ba19e5.avif?t=1775122300\" width=597 height=88 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>還有一點也很重要：在擊敗Boss後，可以與她們分享極緻美好時刻。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/3a40dc23c971de69c77961cf