5d3ba89c71762f.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Perverted Hand</strong> is an exciting roguelite game that blends fast-paced action with hilarious, unpredictable fun! Each run is a fresh experience, face unexpected challenges, and develop your own unique Hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/06155c7fcdbe2a35ba7d9afccfac0e5f.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/5128d966e2ac522404e16fff72b995d8.avif?t=1775122300\" width=421 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to play, just <strong>harass and slap</strong> to win! The game’s core mechanics are simple but <strong>deeply satisfying</strong>. You control a Perverted Hand with an arsenal of slap-based attacks and tricks. Harass your enemies, toy with them, and strike at the perfect moment to claim victory! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/7a3d4b16c4f3389f21ef8ea2a1981a0a.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute, sexy monsters populate every corner of the stage, adding a mix of humor to your adventures. Whether you're taking on sassy succubi, naughty slime, or other whimsical foes, each monster is uniquely designed to challenge and entertain. These flirty and fun characters will keep you on your toes as you strategize your next move! <br> <br>The game features a robust <strong>7 primary stats system</strong> that lets you build your hand’s power in many direction. From Strength to Luck, each stat plays a vital role in shaping how you handle different enemies and bosses.  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/6e8549dcac493feca42fafae916ae079.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/08f35d9baf91e373738e6a87a042604b.avif?t=1775122300\" width=342 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many skills with different usage</strong>, the hand’s potential is limitless. Upgrade a variety of abilities, from flashy attacks to clever evasions, and mix and match them to suit your strategy. Whether you’re focusing on brutal damage or tactical control, the flexibility in skill combinations ensures that every playthrough is fantastic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/eaf02ea92bea3d55f3b0d96c52b11ae5.mp4?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/779091a3001ded0d90817bf4e7dc1632.avif?t=1775122300\" width=342 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many items support rich gameplay</strong>, offering countless ways to enhance your hand’s abilities. Collect powerful artifacts that unlock new synergies and alter your combat tactics. These items aren’t just for show—they can drastically change how you approach each fight, giving you an edge against the game’s toughest challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.poster.avif?t=1775122300\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d1690782338a4.webm?t=1775122300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264850/extras/c1bbab012bc7181a117d169